```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "Logic Function Implementation Schema",
  "description": "Describes the structure for implementing a logic function using the Decoder method.",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "functionName": {
      "description": "The name of the implemented logic function, e.g., '1-bit Full Adder Sum'",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "inputVariables": {
      "description": "A list of the function's input variables.",
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "examples": [
        ["A", "B", "C"]
      ]
    },
    "implementation": {
      "description": "Details about the function's implementation.",
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "method": {
          "description": "The implementation method.",
          "type": "string",
          "const": "Decoder-OR"
        },
        "decoder": {
          "description": "Information about the decoder used.",
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "type": {
              "description": "The type of decoder, e.g., '3-to-8', '2-to-4'.",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "inputs": {
              "description": "Which variables the decoder's inputs are connected to.",
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "string"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": ["type", "inputs"]
        },
        "orGateInputs": {
          "description": "A list of the decoder outputs connected to the OR gate. Each value corresponds to a minterm.",
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "mintermIndices": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "integer",
                "minimum": 0
              }
            },
            "decoderOutputs": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^Y[0-9]+$"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": ["mintermIndices", "decoderOutputs"]
        }
      },
      "required": ["method", "decoder", "orGateInputs"]
    },
    "booleanExpression": {
      "description": "The expression of the logic function as a sum of minterms.",
      "type": "string",
      "examples": ["F(A,B,C) = Σm(1, 4, 7)"]
    }
  },
  "required": ["functionName", "inputVariables", "implementation", "booleanExpression"]
}
```

**Ví dụ một đối tượng JSON theo cấu trúc trên:**

```json
{
  "functionName": "1-bit Full Adder Sum",
  "inputVariables": ["A", "B", "Cin"],
  "implementation": {
    "method": "Decoder-OR",
    "decoder": {
      "type": "3-to-8",
      "inputs": ["A", "B", "Cin"]
    },
    "orGateInputs": {
      "mintermIndices": [1, 2, 4, 7],
      "decoderOutputs": ["Y1", "Y2", "Y4", "Y7"]
    }
  },
  "booleanExpression": "S(A, B, Cin) = Σm(1, 2, 4, 7)"
}
```
